Package org.openehr.rm.common.change_control

Interface ImportedVersion

All Superinterfaces:
Version
public interface ImportedVersion extends Version
Versions whose content is an `ORIGINAL_VERSION` copied from another location; this class inherits `_commit_audit_` and `_contribution_` from `VERSION`, providing imported versions with their own audit trail and Contribution, distinct from those of the imported `ORIGINAL_VERSION`.
